sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant User as User / Dashboard
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ODHWebhook as ODH Webhook<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ODHCtrl as ODH Notebook Controller
    participant NBCtrl as Notebook Controller
    participant Gateway as Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Notebook as Notebook Pod<br/>8888/TCP HTTP

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over User,Notebook: Flow 1: Notebook Creation (Auth-Enabled)
        User->>K8sAPI: POST Notebook CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>ODHWebhook: Mutating admission<br/>TLS (service CA)
        Note right of ODHWebhook: Injects kube-rbac-proxy sidecar,<br/>resolves ImageStream images,<br/>mounts CA bundles, proxy env,<br/>syncs DSPA/Feast config
        ODHWebhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutated Notebook
        K8sAPI->>ODHWebhook: Validating admission<br/>TLS (service CA)
        ODHWebhook-->>K8sAPI: Validated
        K8sAPI-->>User: Notebook created

        NBCtrl->>K8sAPI: Watch: Notebook CR changed
        NBCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create StatefulSet<br/>SA Token auth
        NBCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Service ({name}:80→8888)<br/>SA Token auth

        ODHCtrl->>K8sAPI: Watch: Notebook CR changed
        ODHCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create HTTPRoute (nb-{ns}-{name})<br/>SA Token auth
        ODHCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create ReferenceGrant<br/>SA Token auth
        ODHCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>SA Token auth
        ODHCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create kube-rbac-proxy Service,<br/>ConfigMap, TLS Secret, CRB
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over User,Notebook: Flow 1 (cont): User Accesses Notebook
        User->>Gateway: GET /notebook/{ns}/{name}<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
        Gateway->>KRBP: Forward via HTTPRoute<br/>HTTPS TLS
        KRBP->>K8sAPI: TokenReview<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
        K8sAPI-->>KRBP: Token valid
        KRBP->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>(get notebooks in {ns})
        K8sAPI-->>KRBP: Access granted
        KRBP->>Notebook: Proxy to 8888<br/>HTTP (localhost)
        Notebook-->>KRBP: Response
        KRBP-->>Gateway: Response
        Gateway-->>User: Response
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over User,Notebook: Flow 2: Idle Notebook Culling
        loop Every IDLENESS_CHECK_PERIOD (default: 1 min)
            NBCtrl->>Notebook: GET /api/kernels<br/>HTTP 8888/TCP
            Notebook-->>NBCtrl: Kernel list (activity timestamps)
            NBCtrl->>Notebook: GET /api/terminals<br/>HTTP 8888/TCP
            Notebook-->>NBCtrl: Terminal list
        end
        Note right of NBCtrl: If idle > CULL_IDLE_TIME (default: 1440 min)
        NBCtrl->>K8sAPI: Patch Notebook annotation:<br/>kubeflow-resource-stopped
        NBCtrl->>K8sAPI: Scale StatefulSet replicas=0
    end

    rect rgb(255, 230, 255)
        Note over User,Notebook: Flow 3: DSPA Pipeline Secret Injection
        ODHCtrl->>K8sAPI: Read DSPA CR (named "dspa")<br/>in notebook namespace
        ODHCtrl->>K8sAPI: Read S3 credential Secret<br/>(from DSPA spec)
        ODHCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create/Update ds-pipeline-config Secret<br/>(Elyra pipeline runtime config)
    end
